-- Bresnan Broadband Plans Debt Sale to Fund Cablevision Systems Acquisition
-- B y   S a p n a   M a h e s h w a r i
-- 2010-11-29T14:42:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-29/bresnan-broadband-plans-debt-to-help-fund-cablevision-purchase.html
Bresnan Broadband Holdings LLC plans
to sell $250 million of eight-year senior notes through BBHI
Acquisition LLC to help finance its purchase by Cablevision
Systems Corp., according to a person familiar with the
transaction.  Proceeds will be used, along with borrowings under a senior
secured credit line and an equity contribution from a
Cablevision unit, to finance the acquisition of Bresnan
Broadband and provide it with working capital, said the person,
who declined to be identified because terms arenâ€™t set.   The notes will be marketed from today through Dec. 1, the
person said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
